<P>
PREP PLAYOFFS AT A GLANCE; CITY SECTION TENNIS INDIVIDUAL FINALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GREG SANDOVAL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today's schedule (at the Racquet Centre, Studio City, 2 p.m.): Singles -- 
Dylan Mann, Woodland Hills Taft, vs. Robert Williams, Dorsey. Doubles -- Oliver 
Catlin-Jeff Manson, Palisades, vs.Jason Ebin-Daniel Elperin, Palisades. 
</P>
<P>
 Last year's champions: Singles -- Rafael Huerta, Chatsworth. Doubles -- 
Catlin-Manson, Palisades. 
