SOUTHERN SECTION PLAYOFFS; BASEBALL, SOFTBALL START TIMES ALTERED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Southern Section office announced Wednesday some changes that will affect 
county teams in this weekend's baseball and softball championship games. 
</P>
<P>
 In baseball, Saturday's Division V game between Calvary Chapel and Sierra 
Madre Maranatha at Blair Field in Long Beach has been moved from 2 p.m. to 11 
a.m. 
</P>
<P>
 In softball, the Division II game between Fullerton and La Puente Bishop Amat 
at Mayfair Park in Lakewood has been moved from Friday to Saturday at 7:30 p.m. 
to accommodate Bishop Amat graduation ceremonies Friday night. 
</P>
<P>
 As a result, the Division I final between Marina and Foothill has been moved 
from Saturday to Friday at 7:30 p.m. at Mayfair Park. 
</P>
