 The Angels have been trying to trade Smith for weeks, according to several 
clubs, but it was only this week that the Orioles expressed serious interest. 
</P>
<P>
 If Smith is traded, the Angels will move Jim Edmonds into left field to 
platoon with Bo Jackson. The Angels then would call up J.T. Snow from triple-A 
Vancouver, where he is hitting .294 with eight home runs, to let him play first 
