KABC 16.3 5."The Substitute Wife" KNBC 15.8 6.Seinfeld KNBC 15.6 7.The Simpsons 
KTTV 14.8 8.These Friends of Mine KABC 14.7 9."Angels: Mysterious Messengers" 
KNBC 14.5 10. Frasier KNBC 14.0 Weekly Averages 
</P>
