</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 CoCensys Inc.: The Irvine developer of neuropharmaceutical products reported a 
first-quarter loss of $4.6 million, or 50 cents a share, which included a 
onetime charge of $2 million advanced to an affiliate. That compared to a loss 
of $2.2 million, or 27 cents a share, for the first quarter of 1993. The 
company reported no revenue. 
</P>
