<TEXT>
<P>
 Mike Metzler -- Inaccurate information on the military service of Mike 
Metzler, a Democratic contender in the 69th Assembly District, was included in 
Sunday's election section on Page V10. Metzler is the son of a Marine veteran 
but was never in the Marines himself. 
</P>
