<TEXT>
<P>
 Muhammad shooting -- Yahoshuah Ben Sadic was misidentified as a bodyguard of 
Khallid Abdul Muhammad in a Times photo caption May 30 showing Muhammad being 
assisted by several men after he was shot. Sadic, founder of the Pomona-based 
Nation of Israel, says he is not a member of the Nation of Islam. 
