</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Chavez dedication -- A story in the May 26 edition of The Times incorrectly 
stated that the city of Lynwood dedicated an access road and a local hospital 
to honor the late labor leader Cesar Chavez. Only the access road leading to 
the hospital, St. Francis Medical Center, was renamed in honor of Chavez. 
</P>
